### #1: Ulysses + Workflow + Pythonista + GitHub = Happy blogging 

Aim of this side project is automate new blog entry creation using following tools:
- Ulysses - editing post in markdown
- Workflow - delegating *"Share with ..."* to Pythonista
- Pythonista - modification of original markdown post and uploading to GitHub
- Github - GitHub used as backend with Lektor static blog generator

Project source code can be found in this [gist](link).
